          <h3 style="margin-top:0">Built for UAE conditions</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--muted)">Sandy soil and heat require adaptive strategies. Our approach focuses on low-water irrigation, soil amendments, and scheduling based on plant stress rather than a fixed timer. The robots are designed to be simple, rugged, and easy to use by farmers and community gardens.</p>

          <ul style="margin-top:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7">
